This code is not being developed with exhaustive test suites, so be warned. What is being run?

Migrate your database
=====================

rake dm:migrate
rake dm:migrate RAILS_ENV=test
rake dm_migrate_down VERSION=nnn
rake dm_migrate_down VERSION=nnn RAILS_ENV=test

Running the tests that do exist
===============================

rake rcov:all

(you can find the coverage report in the coverage directory)